Class ChargingStation

java.lang.Object
fr.tp.inf112.projects.robotsim.model.Component
fr.tp.inf112.projects.robotsim.model.ChargingStation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Figure, Visitable, Serializable
public class ChargingStation extends Component
Represents a charging station in the robot simulation. A charging station can charge robots and manage their charging behavior.
